body_html:
@allenlavoie

The next step would be to narrow down and figure out which transitively included header from const_op.h is causing problems;

My tracking history

  1. <tensorflow/cc/ops/const_op.h>
  2. <tensorflow/cc/framework/ops.h>
  3. <tensorflow/core/framework/tensor.h>
  4. <tensorflow/core/lib/core/refcount.h>

As long as I include recount.h, the image return by imread will become empty. However, include <tensorflow/core/platform/logging.h> do not effect the resutls, this is weird. Do not looks like it is caused by #define.
